dct_description_sm: This point shapefile represents Computer Resources for New Orleans, LA in 2018. It lists local libraries and community organizations that will allow you to use computers free of charge. Some locations also offer the following resources: Wi-fi, Printing, Internet, iPad rental, Classes, and special areas for kids and teens. This file was downloaded on December, 2018 by NYU Data Services. It was originally represented on the New Orleans Open Data Socrata portal as catalog record vaaq-p3ar
dct_title_s: Computer Resources for New Orleans, LA, 2018
